radiographic_examinations.findings: Trace right pleural effusion; mild intra and extrahepatic biliary ductal dilatation; 0.4 cm T2 hypointense filling defect in the distal common bile duct concerning for retained stone; pancreas normal in signal intensity and bulk; no pancreatic lesions; kidneys with subcentimeter T2 hyperintense cortical hyperintensities likely consistent with cysts.
